data.text:
IMPORTANT NOTES, PLEASE READ

These images are photographs of the actual records - these are NOT mock-ups. With that said, and with any colorful vinyl record we design, we CAN NOT guarantee they will look exactly like this, and no two records will be exactly the same, (we open a few samples and photograph the most consistent pattern we observe). Please keep that in mind when purchasing.

This release is currently in transit to our warehouse, and will begin shipping the middle of next week, and may take a week or so to ship,depending on the time your order was placed. Please be patient, once your order ships you will get tracking information. Please be aware that Priority Mail orders WILL SHIP FIRST, so if this is needed ASAP for a gift then please choose Priority Mail. This release, upon request, can be shipped outside of the jacket to avoid seam splits. This album comes mailed inside of the jacket sealed with shrink wrap on the outside. We do not have any extra jackets for this release in case of minor damage by the USPS in transit.
